front.title: •I'm Getting Pretty Good At This
front.gametext: If Finn and either Poe or Rey are in a battle together, you may add two battle destiny. OR Deploy Finn aboard any starship or vehicle from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.
front.lore: Starship blaster, often slung in turret mounts to take advantage of light weight and quick targeting motions. Installed on many starships including the Millennium Falcon.
